query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('api',
'append',
'combobox',
'datepicker',
'dynamic',
'google-maps-api-3',
'gridview',
'html-table',
'operating-system',
'python-3.x',
'ruby-on-rails-5',
'struct',
'xml');
